metadata.name: Bus Stop
metadata.description:
Bus Stop, is the first piece created by Mikey featuring Reginald the Roo.

The piece is a digital vector illustration, depicting Reggie sitting at the nearest bus stop, awaiting a ride to meet his companion Rip for coffee a few blocks away.

Included in this piece is "The Crown". Head to the "A Quiet World - Bidders Editions" collection to read the on-chain lore!
